					<ul>
						<li>The commander of a mercenary band called the<br>Shadewolves who were betrayed and annihilated<br>by the Empire. This left him a shell of a man<br>who gave up everything in the name of revenge.<br>Where he goes, dark rumors follow.</li>
					</ul>
