					Deals wind damage to the target and nearby enemies,<br>inflicts bleeding, and activates "Skill Shift" if the attack<br>connects. Phase II adds an additional 3% increase to<br>the entire team's water resistance for 20 seconds,<br>while Phase III also grants all teammates<br>a one-use shield that nullifies damage less<br>than 20% of the user's maximum HP.<br>This does not stack with any other shields.
